Blog::Manager

A simple, extensible, plugin-based blog manager written in Perl.

INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

	perl Makefile.PL
	make
	make test
	make install

SUPPORT AND DOCUMENTATION

For more information, check the 'Changes' file and the POD data.

